Description: Gulf General Cooperative Insurance (known as: Gulf General) is a public company, listed on Saudi Stock Exchange “Tadawul” (TDWL) since February 2010. Gulf General operates within the Insurance sector focusing on Multi-line Insurance. Gulf General is based in Jeddah, Saudi Arabia and was established in December 2009.
